title: No 5G on Pixel 5 when using "Free Mobile" in France.
content:
Hi Google / Community mods,

Can you confirm when 5G will be enabled on Pixel 5 for carrier "Free Mobile" in France?

5G works just fine if I root my device and modify the carrier policy in EFI but I don't want to use my device rooted on a daily basis.

So please let us know when Google will update Pixel 5 to enable 5G for "Free Mobile" ?

Many thanks,
Mat
